  "text": "The idea to consider TM as the essential part of the cochlea transduction exists in a variety of published articles [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Some of them also considered the traveling waves propagated in the radial direction in TM [CITATION_4] . We generalized this idea to the space-time filtering concept, hypothesizing the existence of the molecular filter, which is able to evaluate the traveling wave parameters from the endolymph molecule orientation in the close vicinity of the stereocilia tops.",
